{"tid":2261182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國如何透過聯合國，直接改變全世界對「人權」的定義？","createTime":"2020-10-28T06:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T10:25:52.000Z","uid":66324,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a5432c1a40f3108853899dbaf47f6d4834cecbb7","tid":2261182,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/142058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F142058&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=868097eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/142058</a>"},{"pid":"e03bc294c6b48fb24c8718bcb844a19430d3e55f","tid":2261182,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"784a41eb0426a9825601f97bc914bc1da6e656df","tid":2261182,"uid":66324,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;10月14日美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）發文抨擊，中國、俄羅斯等國家當選聯合國人權理事會今（2020）年改選的15席代表。輿論大多認為這是做賊喊捉賊、破壞人權的國家進入聯合國等。台灣不在聯合國內，對這新聞沒特別的看法，頂多就開爆米花看戲。<br />\n<br />\n然而，中國真的有破壞人權嗎？<br />\n<br />\n讀者看到這問題別嚇一跳。這事實上是中國近幾年全力投入聯合國的重點項目之一：直接改變全世界對人權的定義，而這跟習近平思想直接相關。&quot;"},{"pid":"243ae3e9be9200a5a10d29a5617619851cad27db","tid":2261182,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:43:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f65398b7d0f22bcac70ef2d6e06ac726ba2d370a","tid":2261182,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"你d有用po唔會有人幫你推架啦<br />\n我幫你啦"},{"pid":"8fefaef8dfb7121d0ad4811385ce88d8a193600a","tid":2261182,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5432c1a40f3108853899dbaf47f6d4834cecbb7","tid":2261182,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/142058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/