&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=9820c3b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8199719/Dr-Tedros-Ghebreyesus-career-politician-running-China-centric-WHO.html</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合國幕後係由World Economic Forum話事，聯合國嘅重要支持者David Rockefeller係中國共產黨長期合作夥伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">The social experiment in China under. Chairman Mao's leadership is one of the most important and successful in human history. How extensively China opens up and how the world interprets and reacts to the social innovations and life styles she has developed is certain to have a profound impact on the future of many nations.</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/1973/08/10/archives/from-a-china-traveler.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1973%2F08%2F10%2Farchives%2Ffrom-a-china-traveler.html&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=3036ec21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/1973/08/10/archives/from-a-china-traveler.html</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合國Secretary General Antonio Guterres 係個socialist嚟，佢一直執行緊WEF定落嚟嘅agenda，而家講緊嘅The Great Reset <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weforum.org/great-reset/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fgreat-reset%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=4561f47b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weforum.org/great-reset/</a>"},{"pid":"fd98bf595d918c7173a94634e24d6fb06ac58c47","tid":2261182,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"撳錯咗負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a1c96d61bae3e575006d9c8867e2673c7104ae","tid":2261182,"uid":253608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite